之理由，抗告於臺灣高等法院。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　9 　　月　　7 　　日\r\n                                  書記官  白豐瑋","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KLDM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c668%2c20220907%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KLDM,111,聲,668,20220907,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"668","JDATE":"20220907","JTITLE":"束縛身體處分"}